OL,3,CJersey nurseries struggle to operate
OL,4,Cwith lack of qualified staff
OL,6,FA nursery manager in Jersey is calling
OL,7,Fon the Government to offer more
OL,8,Fflexible training courses to ease
OL,9,Fstaffing shortages.
OL,11,FNicky Crenan, preschool team leader at
OL,12,FLittle Oaks Nursery, says some of
OL,13,Ftheir employees are studying Level
OL,14,FThree courses, which will help them
OL,15,Faddress the gap in qualified
OL,16,Fpractitioners.
OL,18,FHowever, she says classes are not
OL,19,Favailable outside of the workday,
OL,20,Fmaking the issue of having enough
OL,21,Fstaff to safely run a nursery worse.
