OL,3,CJersey nurseries struggle to operate
OL,4,Cwith lack of qualified staff
OL,6,FNicky explains: "We have to put more
OL,7,Funqualified staff onto courses that
OL,8,Fare in the day and we then have to
OL,9,Ffind cover. You've also got sickness,
OL,10,Fother people are poorly and you
OL,11,Fhaven't got enough to cover, so that's
OL,12,Fa big challenge.
OL,14,F"Everybody's got their groups of
OL,15,Fchildren to look after, they're
OL,16,Flearning through play, and if you
OL,17,Fhaven't got enough people then those
OL,18,Froutines won't happen and the day-to-
OL,19,Fday running of the nursery is really,
OL,20,Freally tricky.
