OL,3,CJersey nurseries struggle to operate
OL,4,Cwith lack of qualified staff
OL,6,F"If you haven't got the ratios then
OL,7,Fyou wouldn't be able to open.
OL,8,FFortunately, it's not impacted us in
OL,9,Fthat way at the moment, but that's not
OL,10,Fto say it won't in the future."
OL,12,FNicky adds that any government work to
OL,13,Frecruit and retain early years staff
OL,14,Fmust show them that they are valued.
