OL,3,CJersey nurseries struggle to operate
OL,4,Cwith lack of qualified staff
OL,6,FShe explains: "It also needs to be a
OL,7,Flovely job to do. It needs to be able
OL,8,Fto encourage people into the workplace
OL,9,Fand offer incentives to do that. Pay
OL,10,Fis one, hours, not having to cover
OL,11,Fpeople when they're off all the time
OL,12,Fand being really burnt out.
OL,14,F"It's not an easy job and the hours
OL,15,Faren't 9-5 ... we're in here from 7
OL,16,Fo'clock in the morning, setting up the
OL,17,Fnursery and making sure it's ready for
OL,18,Fthe children.
