OL,3,CJersey nurseries struggle to operate
OL,4,Cwith lack of qualified staff
OL,6,F"You don't leave at 3 o'clock and have
OL,7,Fnothing else to do. There's lots of
OL,8,Foutside work to do ... we don't just
OL,9,Fsit and play with the children all
OL,10,Fday, even though that is very
OL,11,Fimportant."
OL,13,FFiona Vacher, Executive Director of
OL,14,FJersey Child Care Trust charity, says
OL,15,Fthat the key to addressing staff
OL,16,Fshortages is collaboration, as she
OL,17,Fstresses good quality childcare needs
OL,18,Fto be prioritised.
