OL,3,CJersey nurseries struggle to operate
OL,4,Cwith lack of qualified staff
OL,6,FFiona adds: "It's an island-wide issue
OL,7,Fand it's one we're seeing nationally
OL,8,Fas well. We need to work together as
OL,9,Fthe voluntary, private and government
OL,10,Fsectors to think about how we can make
OL,11,Fthis better for people.
OL,13,F"We want people skipping to work,
OL,14,Fhappy staff, so that children are
OL,15,Fhaving a very happy experience as well
OL,16,Fand families feel supported."
